Package pls.expression

Class Operator

  • java.lang.Object
    • pls.expression.Operator
  • public class Operator
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for creating lambda functions that can be registered with the parser as operator generators.

    Methods in this class can be used to create operator functions that can be registered with the expression parser. For example: 

    
    Parser.registerOperator("==", 8, Operator.createRelationalGenerator("==", (l, r) -> Objects.equals(l, r)));
    Author:
    Peter Smith
    See Also:
    Parser
